<HEAD>For Release at 6 p.m. EST - time set by source</HEAD>
<HEAD>Violent Crime Up 5 Percent In First Half Of This Year, FBI Says</HEAD>
<HEAD>Retransmitting a0686 to fix cycle designator.</HEAD>
